title: Three in a Row
---
body:

Same man,different fish! Anthony scores a hat-trick and tags out with another beauty of 9lbs, taken on the worm. A few fish have been caught since the last flood with a steady trickle of salmon scaling the river all the time. Spinning has been the most successful method. Prospects are great as the water is dropping slowly, tides are building and cloudier conditions are forecast for the coming days.<br>

